    <div class="card">
      <h2>Project Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Community Canvas Bolton is a proposed public art project where local residents,
        young people, artists, community groups, and visitors can contribute to a shared
        painted canvas in Bolton town centre.
      </p>
      <p>
        The project aims to create a colourful, welcoming and community-led artwork that
        celebrates local identity, creativity and public participation.
      </p>
